ğŸ–¥ï¸ Screenshot Hygiene and Command Logging
This might sound like overkill, but hereâ€™s how I maintained evidence discipline:
ğŸ“¸ Screenshots

Saved into folders named by IP/hostname (e.g., 192.168.15.23 or DC01)
